{
  "stem": "490.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I'll never forget his name, his name was Jeremiah Zaczinski.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I'll never forget this [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The reason I remember him, because he was my closest friend.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he was not-- because he had a mind like a-- now, today, I understand.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "At the time, we didn't know there was such a thing as an IQ.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He, he could-- he had a photographic mind.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And whenever the teacher used to say something, he used to just automatically, he never forget it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we always, whenever we missed something, we came to him, and he remembered.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they called up, and he walks out.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And he says, yes, it's me who sleeps there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They put him the middle of the street, middle of-- in the center, and they shot him.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They shot him dead.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Later we found out that on the top of his bunk, where he was sleeping, between the cracks, they found a, a $5 bill that somebody put it there.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He didn't have any $5.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He didn't know what it meant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But somehow, somebody was able to put it there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] so, and as a matter of fact, we buried-- we buried him right outside, you know, the gate, without even no big deal, and-- So if you want to know how life was there, while we were working, I mean, we had freedom inside the factory.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But we had to do your work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Like, I was working at a steel mill.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I had to-- where they, they, they melt steel.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
